{
  "stem": "27390.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We didn't know anything about it, what this, what this place is.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "What it's-- why they are wearing these pajamas.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We stayed there like this in the train, in the wagon, for about two hours.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And all of a sudden we heard noises coming with dogs, and shouting, and screaming.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The doors opened, and they started shouting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They started hitting us with the rifle butts.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Aus, aus, aus, schnell, schnell, schnell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And the dogs were barking, and the screaming.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Anyway it was such a mix up, we ran-- we, we fell off these wagons.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And then they, they, they, they separated men one side, women the other side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "My mother and my sister were pushed aside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And the last words my mother said to me was look after Yitzhak.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "That's my younger brother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were pushed along with a crowd of people till somebody came up to me, and he said in Yiddish, he said, if he asks how old you are, you should say you are 18.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my brother asked this man, where are we?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he said, you are in Auschwitz, he said.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know what that word means, Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he said to-- my brother asked him, what's so special about Auschwitz?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he said, you'll find out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were pushed along till finally we came to a place, and they pushed us into a barrack.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they took us out from this barrack, and we were put in-- there was this assessment standing there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And rechts, links, right, left, and I was-- I made myself look nice and straight, and my brother as well.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We managed to get through to the right, the side that the people are staying, were staying alive.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
